Introduction:
This programs renders Cow and add texture to it. Other models available with the package can also be rendered
but accurate texturing is implemented for Cow model only.

Controls:
keyboard
+ : zoom in
- : zoom out
l : wire frame
p : point cloud

shift + mouse-left-key : move camera inward/outward.
Mouse right click : pop-up menu


Install SOIL libray
Compile using Makefile
Run texture application

